---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const siteName = "Joel Johnston",
    siteUrl = "https://www.joelj.ca",
    contactEmail = "me@joelj.ca",
    lastUpdated = "November 1, 2025";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
    <main
        class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-12 prose prose-invert prose-headings:mt-8 pt-20 text-lg"
    >
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold pt-10">Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

        <section id="introduction" class="mt-10">
            <h3>1. Introduction</h3>
            <p>
                Welcome to <strong>{siteName}</strong> (&quot;we,&quot; &quot;our,&quot;
                or &quot;us&quot;). Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy
                Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and protect your information
                when you visit our website {" "}
                <a href={siteUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                    {siteUrl}
                </a>{" "}
                (the &quot;Site&quot;). By using the Site, you agree to this Privacy
                Policy. If you do not agree, please do not use our website.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section id="information-we-collect" class="mt-10">
            <h3>2. Information We Collect</h3>
            <h4 class="mt-6">a. Information You Provide</h4>
            <p>
                We collect personal information that you voluntarily provide,
                such as when you:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-inside list-disc">
                <li>Fill out forms or request information through HubSpot;</li>
                <li>Subscribe to our newsletter; or</li>
                <li>Contact us via email or web forms.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>This information may include:</p>
            <ul class="list-inside list-disc">
                <li>Name</li>
                <li>Email address</li>
                <li>Phone number</li>
                <li>Company name (if applicable)</li>
                <li>Any other information you choose to share</li>
            </ul>

            <h4 class="mt-6">b. Automatically Collected Information</h4>
            <p>
                When you visit our Site, we automatically collect certain data,
                including:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-inside list-disc">
                <li>IP address;</li>
                <li>Browser type and version;</li>
                <li>Device type and operating system;</li>
                <li>Pages visited, time spent, and referring websites; and</li>
                <li>General (non-precise) geographic location.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                This information is collected using cookies and similar
                technologies (see Section 4).
            </p>
        </section>

        <section id="how-we-use" class="mt-10">
            <h3>3. How We Use Your Information</h3>
            <ul class="list-inside list-disc">
                <li>Respond to your inquiries and requests;</li>
                <li>Improve and optimize our website and services;</li>
                <li>
                    Send marketing and promotional communications (only if
                    you’ve opted in);
                </li>
                <li>
                    Analyze website traffic and user behavior via Google
                    Analytics;
                </li>
                <li>
                    Manage customer relationships and communications through
                    HubSpot; and
                </li>
                <li>Comply with legal obligations.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section id="cookies" class="mt-10">
            <h3>4. Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h3>
            <h4 class="mt-6">a. Cookies</h4>
            <p>
                Cookies are small data files stored on your device that help
                improve user experience and website performance. You can disable
                cookies in your browser settings, but some features of the Site
                may not function properly as a result.
            </p>
            <h4 class="mt-6">b. Google Analytics</h4>
            <p>
                We use Google Analytics to understand how visitors interact with
                our website. Google Analytics collects information such as your
                IP address, browser type, and pages visited. This information is
                aggregated before analysis.
            </p>
            <p>
                You can opt out of Google Analytics tracking by installing the {
                    " "
                }
                <a
                    href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                >
                    Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on
                </a>
                . Learn more in Google’s {" "}
                <a
                    href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                >
                    Partner Sites policy
                </a>
                .
            </p>

            <h4 class="mt-6">c. HubSpot</h4>
            <p>
                We use HubSpot for CRM, marketing automation, and analytics.
                HubSpot may collect information through cookies and forms to
                help us understand visitor behavior and manage communications.
                You can learn more about HubSpot’s privacy practices here:
            </p>
            <p>
                <a
                    href="https://legal.hubspot.com/privacy-policy"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                >
                    https://legal.hubspot.com/privacy-policy
                </a>
            </p>
        </section>

        <section id="sharing" class="mt-10">
            <h3>5. Sharing Your Information</h3>
            <p>
                We do not sell or rent your personal data. We may share
                information only with:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-inside list-disc">
                <li>
                    Service providers (e.g., website hosting, analytics, CRM)
                    who help operate our business;
                </li>
                <li>
                    Legal authorities, if required by law or to protect our
                    rights; and
                </li>
                <li>
                    Successors or acquirers, in the event of a business transfer
                    or merger.
                </li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                All third-party partners are required to handle your data
                securely and in accordance with applicable laws.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section id="retention" class="mt-10">
            <h3>6. Data Retention</h3>
            <p>
                We retain personal data only as long as necessary to fulfill the
                purposes outlined in this policy, unless a longer retention
                period is required by law. You may request deletion of your data
                at any time by contacting us (see Section 12).
            </p>
        </section>

        <section id="security" class="mt-10">
            <h3>7. Security</h3>
            <p>
                We use reasonable technical and organizational measures to
                protect your information from unauthorized access, alteration,
                disclosure, or destruction. However, no internet-based service
                is completely secure.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section id="your-rights" class="mt-10">
            <h3>8. Your Rights</h3>
            <p>Depending on your location, you may have the right to:</p>
            <ul class="list-inside list-disc">
                <li>Access, correct, or delete your personal data;</li>
                <li>Withdraw consent to marketing communications;</li>
                <li>Object to or restrict data processing; and</li>
                <li>Request data portability.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                To exercise any of these rights, contact us at {" "}
                <a href={`mailto:${contactEmail}`}>{contactEmail}</a>.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section id="intl-transfers" class="mt-10">
            <h3>9. International Data Transfers</h3>
            <p>
                If you are accessing our Site from outside your country, please
                note that your information may be transferred to and processed
                in other countries, including the United States, where data
                protection laws may differ from those in your jurisdiction.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section id="third-party-links" class="mt-10">
            <h3>10. Third-Party Links</h3>
            <p>
                Our Site may contain links to third-party websites. We are not
                responsible for their privacy practices or content. Please
                review their policies before providing any personal information.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section id="children" class="mt-10">
            <h3>11. Children’s Privacy</h3>
            <p>
                Our Site is not directed to children under 13 (or 16 in some
                jurisdictions). We do not knowingly collect information from
                children.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section id="contact" class="mt-10">
            <h3>12. Contact Us</h3>
            <p>
                If you have questions or wish to exercise your privacy rights,
                contact us at:
            </p>
            <p>
                <strong>Email:</strong>
                <a href={`mailto:${contactEmail}`}>{contactEmail}</a>
                <br />
                <strong>Website:</strong>{" "}
                <a href={siteUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                    {siteUrl}
                </a>
            </p>
        </section>

        <section id="updates" class="mt-10">
            <h3>13. Updates to This Policy</h3>
            <p>
                We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Any changes will
                be posted on this page with the updated date.
            </p>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>
